OL,3,CSurvivors of coercive control call for
OL,4,Cmedia access to family courts
OL,6,FAlmost thirty thousand decisions have
OL,7,Fbeen taken over two years in the
OL,8,Ffamily courts in Northern Ireland -
OL,9,Falmost 17,000 of which involve family
OL,10,Fhome and domestic violence and
OL,11,Fchildren orders.JSeveral women have
OL,12,Ftold UTV that their experience with
OL,13,Fthis part of the legal system - which
OL,14,Fis held behind closed doors - has left
OL,15,Fthem traumatised.
OL,17,FSome allege they were threatened with
OL,18,Fpenal notices, contempt of court, and
OL,19,Fthe potential removal of their
OL,20,Fchildren.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G1/13
