OL,3,CSurvivors of coercive control call for
OL,4,Cmedia access to family courts
OL,6,FThe women, who are also survivors of
OL,7,Fdomestic abuse, cannot be identified
OL,8,Fto preserve their anonymity and that
OL,9,Fof their children.
OL,11,FThey met the victims of crime
OL,12,Fcommissioner at Stormont earlier this
OL,13,Fweek to lobby for a greater level of
OL,14,Ftransparency to ensure victims of
OL,15,Fdomestic abuse and their children are
OL,16,Fbetter protected - including a call
OL,17,Ffor journalists to be allowed to
OL,18,Freport on family proceedings.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G2/13
