OL,3,CSurvivors of coercive control call for
OL,4,Cmedia access to family courts
OL,6,F'Beth' - not her real name - has
OL,7,Fbattled for over two years through the
OL,8,Ffamily courts in Northern Ireland to
OL,9,Fprotect her now three-year-old son
OL,10,Ffrom contact with his father - a drug
OL,11,Faddict and her abuser.
OL,13,FThe 40-year-old alleges she was
OL,14,Fthreatened with penal notices, removal
OL,15,Fof her children and even arrest after
OL,16,Fshe was unable to make certain court
OL,17,Fappearances to care for her son who
OL,18,Fhas complex needs.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G3/13
