OL,3,CSurvivors of coercive control call for
OL,4,Cmedia access to family courts
OL,6,FHer ex-partner she believes was
OL,7,Forchestrating custody proceedings to
OL,8,Fcoercively control her.
OL,10,F''I ended up becoming the criminal in
OL,11,Fmy case where I was trying to
OL,12,Fsafeguard my child and I was being
OL,13,Fstigmatised as a vexatious mother. I
OL,14,Fwas being labelled as a parental
OL,15,Falienator. Implacable hostility was
OL,16,Fused against me. How is this being
OL,17,Fallowed to happen within our judiciary
OL,18,Fsystem in Northern Ireland?,'' she
OL,19,Fclaims.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G4/13
