OL,3,CSurvivors of coercive control call for
OL,4,Cmedia access to family courts
OL,6,F'Beth' added: ''Why are judges putting
OL,7,Fpenal notices on mothers that are
OL,8,Fvictims? You're being told that you'll
OL,9,Fbe held in contempt of court if you
OL,10,Fdon't obey the court order which is a
OL,11,Fforced contact with an abusive parent.
OL,12,FYou're being threatened with a
OL,13,Fresidency order that your child is
OL,14,Fgoing to be removed from your care and
OL,15,Fput under the care of the unsafe
OL,16,Fparent, the abusive parent.''
OL,18,FThe Victims of Crime Commissioner
OL,19,Fagrees reform of the family courts
OL,20,Fneeds urgent attention.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G5/13
