OL,3,CSurvivors of coercive control call for
OL,4,Cmedia access to family courts
OL,6,FGeraldine Hanna plans to carry out
OL,7,Fresearch in this area to determine the
OL,8,Fscale of the problem.
OL,10,F''What we know is of child contact can
OL,11,Fbe another tool for perpetrators to
OL,12,Fuse post-separation. And what we want
OL,13,Fto see in our family courts is the
OL,14,Frecognition and understanding of
OL,15,Fthat,'' said Ms Hanna.
OL,17,F''One of the challenges we have is
OL,18,Fthat the family court system is a
OL,19,Fclosed court so we don't have the same
OL,20,Ftransparency of that system for good
OL,21,Freasons.''
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G6/13
