OL,4,Cmedia access to family courts
OL,6,FThe Justice Minister Naomi Long says
OL,7,Fshe would be keen to have a discussion
OL,8,Fabout the merits of greater
OL,9,Ftransparency, including media access
OL,10,Fto family courts for the media to be
OL,11,Fthere.
OL,13,F''The challenge is how that would come
OL,14,Fabout because obviously these are some
OL,15,Fof the most sensitive personal and
OL,16,Fintimate details which people are
OL,17,Fsharing in family court,'' she said.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G7/13
