OL,3,CSurvivors of coercive control call for
OL,4,Cmedia access to family courts
OL,6,F''So finding a way of maintaining the
OL,7,Fprivacy and dignity of those accessing
OL,8,Fthe family court while at the same
OL,9,Ftime making the public more aware of
OL,10,Fthe processes will, I think, be the
OL,11,Fkey balance.''
OL,13,F'Beth' believes reporters being
OL,14,Fpresent in these types of cases will
OL,15,Fhelp women like her.
OL,17,F''For the media to be there I do
OL,18,Fbelieve that I would have a massive
OL,19,Fimpact on the way judges are
OL,20,Fapproaching cases,'' she said.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G8/13
