OL,3,CSurvivors of coercive control call for
OL,4,Cmedia access to family courts
OL,6,FIn a statement from the office of the
OL,7,Fchief justice, Dame Siobhan Keegan
OL,8,Fsaid she and her judicial colleagues
OL,9,Fwere aware of the ''devastating
OL,10,Fimpact'' on families experiencing
OL,11,Fdomestic abuse and she wanted to
OL,12,Fensure that complainants who have
OL,13,Fsuffered domestic abuse are ''heard,
OL,14,Fsupported and have access to the full
OL,15,Fsuite of special measures and orders
OL,16,Fwhich the court can provide to ensure
OL,17,Fthe protection of them and their
OL,18,Ffamilies''.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G9/13
