OL,6,FShe added: ''The welfare of the child
OL,7,For children is at the forefront in the
OL,8,Fconsideration of any family case and
OL,9,Fthe outcome will depend on the
OL,10,Fspecific circumstances that pertain to
OL,11,Fthat case.
OL,13,F''A range of different factors will be
OL,14,Fconsidered by the Judge including all
OL,15,Fof the evidence provided to the court
OL,16,Fas well as the relevant statute and
OL,17,Fcase law before making their
OL,18,Fdecision.''
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                         G10/13
