OL,6,FThe statement continued that Dame
OL,7,FKeegan has ''long advocated for
OL,8,Ftransparency and greater access to our
OL,9,Fcourt system to promote open justice
OL,10,Fand help the public better understand
OL,11,Fthe complex decisions that judges
OL,12,Fmake''.
