OL,6,F''Following on from the work in 2019
OL,7,Fto pilot media access and reporting of
OL,8,Fcases in the Family Division of the
OL,9,FHigh Court, the shadow Family Justice
OL,10,FBoard asked the Department of Justice
OL,11,Fto consider the necessary policy and
OL,12,Flegislative considerations to support
OL,13,Fmedia access to family cases,'' it
OL,14,Fread.
OL,16,FA scheme to allow reporters into
OL,17,Ffamily court has been piloted within
OL,18,Fthe last number of weeks in England
OL,19,Fand Wales.
